## üìè Performance Optimization

### CSS Purging
- Tailwind automatically purges unused styles in production
- Use dynamic class names carefully to avoid purging issues
- Use safelist in `tailwind.config.ts` for dynamic classes

### Critical CSS
```tsx
// Inline critical styles for above-the-fold content
<style jsx>{`
  .hero-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #DC2626 0%, #B91C1C 100%);
  }
`}</style>
```

This design system ensures consistent visual language, optimal user experience, and maintainable styling across the Palabreo platform while adhering to accessibility standards and performance best practices.